{"tid":562843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人貝澳露營過新年：節省數千元酒店費","createTime":"2018-02-16T09:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T03:46:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5e122c3e1e3ee0c7de0fcf34b2b75b9b18e225","tid":562843,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T09:35:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180216/large/1518766469_b944.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180216%2Flarge%2F1518766469_b944.jpg&h=5255acfe&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180216/large/1518766555_836b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180216%2Flarge%2F1518766555_836b.jpg&h=3df92c98&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180216/large/1518766485_ee0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180216%2Flarge%2F1518766485_ee0b.jpg&h=47c2988d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180216/large/1518766490_35a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180216%2Flarge%2F1518766490_35a6.jpg&h=5ab8f3ce&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貝澳營區近年成為中國旅客露營熱點之一，在大年初一的中午雖然仍未爆滿，但已有不少中國旅客及本港市民前來以露營方式來歡度新年。 <br />\n<br />\n在深圳打工、老家在安徽的潘先生說，今年選擇來香港度歲，為節省數千元酒店費用，所以一家四、五人到貝澳露營。他說許多營區預訂已爆滿，所以只能在不用預訂的草地扎營。他說在香港玩幾天，等人流不多會再上天壇大佛、迪士尼樂園、購物後再回深圳。 <br />\n<br />\n市民李先生與幾位親友年卅晚已在貝澳露營。他說難得與親友一起放年假，所以選擇露營度歲過新年。 <br />\n小朋友李綺琳坐在吊床上搖晃。她說，雖然年卅晚只吃蘿蔔糕和公仔麵，但覺得很開心。她的姨媽還帶備利是，即場派發給她和親友們，為大家帶來不一樣的新年歡樂。<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180216/57840875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180216%2F57840875&d=6R1NWmwuYKdQhY7l7wlf8ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=ad8d477b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180216%2F57840875&h=e17edc61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180216/57840875</a>"},{"pid":"f734553eb99e46408f32421ec73c324cae9677d8","tid":562843,"uid":9193,"like":6,"dislike":21,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T09:36:12.000Z","msg":"最尾張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674fd11954773bb93b503baa5c4d820852c1d623","tid":562843,"uid":72730,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T09:37:05.000Z","msg":"大種乞衣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa3a1e0af81c51b43527c45bb4b258649222238","tid":562843,"uid":3773,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"f734553eb99e46408f32421ec73c324cae9677d8","tid":562843,"uid":9193,"like":6,"dislike":21,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T09:36:12.000Z","msg":"最尾張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T09:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/16/1_year_rent.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F16%2F1_year_rent.png&h=c86a3ee0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bccb2e57eb293f57d425d0ba6586694c20968162","tid":562843,"uid":129664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:01:04.000Z","msg":"蝗國唔係好有錢咩？嗰幾千蚊酒店錢都俾唔起？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一家大細去旅行去到酒店都住唔起仲去嚟把鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc675a6df842f20af4fcb2d9c429101261eede9","tid":562843,"uid